'''''Star Wars: Droids''''', published by [[Dark Horse Comics]], was a series of [[Star Wars comic books|comics]] revolving around [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] and [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]], published in [[1994]]. The logo for ''Star Wars: Droids'' was designed by [[Scott Tice]]. It was followed by a [[Star Wars: Droids (1995)|second series]] of the same name the following year.

